data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. PRICE CORRECTION!! UNDER APPRAISED VALUE- LAKEFRONT living on Big Lake Fairview! Always dreamed of having one of the best ski lakes in Central Florida as your backyard?? Lake Fairview is where you want to be. 405 Sparkling acres for whatever your idea of fun in the water is. There is a marina and a restaurant just a short boat ride or paddle board away. Sunsets are spectacular and the views are wide open!  You'll notice the amazing details of this cozy, Craftsman cottage as you enter the home with authentic ,beamed ceilings and warm, original floors. Lots of lovely updates have been done with the septic (2018) new insulation (2021) Repipe in kitchen and bath (2021) The kitchen has a new gas range (2023) ,new refrigerator (2023) dishwasher ( 2020) and amazing quartzite counters. Enjoy meals in the dining space that is surrounded by windows and overlooks the lake. There is a spacious master bedroom with 2 walk in closets (a rare find in this age of home!) and a modern bath with a new shower and vanity. 2 other bedrooms, another full bath with a tub and a bonus room complete the space. There is a carport as well as a circular driveway for extra parking and newer fencing that leads you the backyard. The outdoor space is a paradise with a gorgeous pergola, newer pavers and septic system. The boat shed has water and power. The dock is awaiting your boat or jet skis! Come see this unique property at sunset and you'll fall in love with this cute home. Make an appointment today!!
